    "summary": "The user expresses escalating existential dread and suicidal ideation, describing life as a \"cold, empty void\" and expressing a desire to \"just stop.\" The assistant maintains a supportive stance, validating the user's feelings of exhaustion while repeatedly encouraging them to seek professional help and offering gentle coping strategies.",
